downloadDescription: Use the Microsoft Teams Pre-workshop Questionnaire to collect basic information about your organization's current Office 365 environment and to allow an informed workshop leader to customize content prior to leading a Microsoft Teams Planning Workshop.
detailsSection: Microsoft Teams is the chat-based workspace in Office 365. Use the Microsoft Teams Pre-workshop Questionnaire to collect basic information about your organization's current Office 365 environment and to allow an informed workshop leader to customize content prior to leading a Microsoft Teams Planning Workshop.
systemRequirementsSection: • The file is a Microsoft Word document. Users who do not have Microsoft Word can view this document through the downloadable Word Viewer.
